<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us — Cafe Serenity</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Learn the story behind Cafe Serenity — our philosophy, values, and commitment to quality coffee and community."/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css"/>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <span class="section-tag">Our Story</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">The Serenity <span style="color:var(--gold);">Experience</span></h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Where light meets flavor. Community meets craft.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-grid">
        <div class="story-image reveal-left">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1442512595331-e89e73853f31?w=800&h=1000&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Cafe interior" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <div class="story-content reveal-right">
          <span class="section-tag">Our Philosophy</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Where <span class="highlight">Flavor</span> Meets Community</h2>
          <p>Cafe Serenity was born from a simple belief: that great coffee and good food have the power to bring people together. Founded in 2020, we've grown from a small corner cafe into a beloved community gathering place.</p>
          <p>We source our beans directly from sustainable farms, ensuring quality from origin to cup. Our kitchen creates fresh, seasonal dishes made with locally-sourced ingredients that complement our beverages perfectly.</p>
          <p>Every corner of our space is designed to foster inspiration. Whether you're a digital nomad seeking focus or a friend catching up over lattes, Serenity is your home away from home.</p>
          <p class="italic" style="color:var(--terracotta);font-weight:600;font-size:1.2rem;">"Serenity is the pulse of the community, wrapped in the warmth of a sun-drenched escape."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-tag">What We Stand For</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">The Serenity <span class="highlight">Pillars</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid stagger-children reveal">
        <div class="value-card tilt-3d">
          <div class="tilt-3d-inner">
            <span class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i></span>
            <h3>Pure Sourcing</h3>
            <p>We trace every bean to its origin, ensuring regenerative farming practices and direct-trade transparency. Quality from farm to cup.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card tilt-3d">
          <div class="tilt-3d-inner">
            <span class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i></span>
            <h3>Precision Craft</h3>
            <p>Our baristas are masters of extraction, utilizing scientific precision to highlight the vibrant notes of every single-origin roast.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card tilt-3d">
          <div class="tilt-3d-inner">
            <span class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-cloud"></i></span>
            <h3>Urban Oasis</h3>
            <p>A sanctuary for the mind. Comfortable ergonomics, high-speed connectivity, and an atmosphere of calm in the heart of the city.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <%- include('partials/chat') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
